cells.content:
SET color red

SET color green GET // return the previous value > "red"

SET x "Hi" XX // XX: add only if KEY EXISTS > x cannot be added

GET x // null

SET color yellow XX // color EXISTS > change color to yellow

GET color

SET color blue NX // NX: add only if KEY NOT EXIST > cannot add in this case

GET color // "yellow": previous value

SET xyz 'BOOOM !!!!' NX // key NOT EXIST > add

GET xyz // "BOOOM !!!!"
